<item>
            <title>[LU-12975] A lot of &quot;quotactl mdtXX failed&quot; messages when use key -v with lfs quota</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12975</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Patch &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12624&quot; title=&quot;DNE3: striped directory allocate stripes by QoS&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-12624&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-12624&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; obdclass: lu_tgt_descs cleanup&quot; introduced a regression causing a bunch of following messages when &quot;lfs quota&quot; is used with key -v:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;quotactl mdt52 failed.
quotactl mdt53 failed.
quotactl mdt54 failed.
quotactl mdt55 failed.
quotactl mdt56 failed.
quotactl mdt57 failed.
quotactl mdt58 failed.
quotactl mdt59 failed.
quotactl mdt60 failed.
quotactl mdt61 failed.
quotactl mdt62 failed.
quotactl mdt63 failed.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This kind of errors should be seen in all sanity-quota tests that use getquota inside.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
